| "2s"                                   | =N+A+D+Px2Sg+Sg                        | =N+A+D+Px2Sg+Pl                        | =N+A+D+Px2Sg+Obv                       |
| "3s"                                   |                                        |                                        | =N+A+D+Px3Sg+Obv                       |
